OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773216518
OL,3,CEyewitnesses describe how 'raging
OL,4,Cinferno' quickly destroyed historic
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,F"It was a bit of a raging inferno,
OL,8,Freally," Caroline said.
OL,10,F"The roof had gone by that stage, and
OL,11,Fall I could see were these massive
OL,12,Fflames and a couple of guys with hoses.
OL,14,F"There was a cherry picker thing, a
OL,15,Fraised platform with a hose, but they
OL,16,Fweren't really making much of a dent
OL,17,Fin it.
OL,19,F"It was it was an extreme fire I mean
OL,20,Fit's not something I've seen before to
OL,21,Fbe honest, so yeah it was horrible."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
