PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773216518
OL,3,CEyewitnesses describe how 'raging
OL,4,Cinferno' quickly destroyed historic
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,F"It's very much part of this area yeah
OL,8,FI mean they've expanded a lot over the
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,F"We take our dogs walking behind that
OL,12,Fevery single day so we hear the
OL,13,Fchildren - it's part of the community
OL,14,Fit's really sad to see something like
OL,15,Fthat just disappear overnight."
OL,17,FErika Pretorius' two-year-old son was
OL,18,Fdue to attend Tigers Nursery on
OL,19,FTuesday, but has been forced to make
OL,20,Falternative arrangements.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
