OL,3,CEyewitnesses describe how 'raging
OL,4,Cinferno' quickly destroyed historic
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian Erika said
OL,8,Fshe was shocked and worried when she
OL,9,Fdiscovered what had happened.
OL,11,F"My son loves going there, he loves
OL,12,Fhis key worker, he was thriving in
OL,13,Fthat setting.
OL,15,F"But now, obviously, with it being
OL,16,Fgone, he's not going to see his
OL,17,Ffavourite person at the nursery.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
