OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773216518
OL,3,CEyewitnesses describe how 'raging
OL,4,Cinferno' quickly destroyed historic
OL,5,Cnursery
OL,7,FCrews from Newbury, Theale,
OL,8,FHungerford, Mortimer and Whitley Wood
OL,9,Fwere sent to the scene, together with
OL,10,Fa crew from Hampshire and Isle of
OL,11,FWight Fire and Rescue Service.
OL,13,FNo-one was inside at the time of the
OL,14,Fblaze.
OL,16,FThe cause of the fire is still not
OL,17,Fknown.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
